# Mobile (Expo → native App Store)

- Router: `apps/mobile/app/` (Expo Router). Auth → onboarding birth → `(tabs)`
- Tema: `constants/theme.ts` + `components/ui.tsx`
- **Firebase:** auth, profil, harita kaydı, partner, jeton — `lib/firebase-*.ts`, `lib/birth-service.ts`, `lib/auth.tsx`
- **AI API:** yalnızca `lib/ai-api.ts` + `lib/ai-service.ts`; base URL `EXPO_PUBLIC_AI_API_URL` (`lib/config.ts`)
- **App Store:** `EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_ENV=production` + HTTPS `EXPO_PUBLIC_AI_API_URL` + Firebase `EXPO_PUBLIC_*`
- **Yerel native test:** `development` + LAN IP AI API → `npm run ios:prebuild` → Xcode ⌘R
- Auth state: `lib/auth.tsx` + Firebase Auth
- Doğum formu: `components/BirthForm.tsx` — harita `birth-service.ts` (REST `/me/birth` kullanılmaz)
- Monetizasyon: `lib/monetization.ts` (Firebase jeton)
- Ortam: `app.config.js` + `EXPO_PUBLIC_*`
- Native plugin: `plugins/withNativeIosStandalone.js` (gömülü bundle)
- `@asto/shared` import et; sabitleri mobile içinde tekrar tanımlama
